.row-fluid
	.span12
		#carousel-front-page.carousel.slide
			.carousel-inner
				.item.active.section
					.row
						.span6
							h3 What is Redfly?
							ul
								li Redfly helps you organize and align individual networks around organizational goals.
								li Redfly is a business contact management software that helps you build your <b>institutional memory</b> by sharing and organizing important contacts within your organization. 
								li We allow you take advantage of your organization's existing social capital.
						.span6
							img.img-responsive(src="/images/collabnet.png")

				.item.section-colored
					.row
						.span6
							h3 Get e-mail updates for new contacts
							ul
								li Redfly sends you weekly e-mails with new contacts added to your institutional network each week. 
								li We allow you to stay on top of business opportunities and network growth.
						.span6
							img.img-responsive(src="/images/emailupdates.png")

				.item.section
					.row
						.span6
							img.img-responsive(src="/images/syncgmail.png")
						.span6
							h3 Easy login and syncing with Gmail and LinkedIn
							ul
								li Imports your contacts through outgoing e-mails.
								li Augment your current contacts with up-to-date LinkedIn information.
								li Keep private contacts private with personal controls.
			a.left.carousel-control(href="#carousel-front-page", data-slide="prev")
				i.icon-chevron-left
			a.right.carousel-control(href="#carousel-front-page", data-slide="next")
				i.icon-chevron-right
			ol.carousel-indicators
				li.active(data-target="#carousel-front-page", data-slide-to="0")
				li(data-target="#carousel-front-page", data-slide-to="1")
				li(data-target="#carousel-front-page", data-slide-to="2")



		.span12
			.row
				br
			.row
				.span4
					h4
						i.icon-tags
						span &nbsp; Tag to Classify
					p Tag contacts with custom labels by project, event, or even extracurricular interest. Redly allows you to create a custom tag dictionary and tag groups.
				.span4
					h4
						i.icon-search
						span &nbsp; Search to Discover 
					p Easily locate contacts with a specific expertise or background and ask colleagues for an introduction through Redfly.
				.span4
					h4
						i.icon-exchange
						span &nbsp; Recommend and Request
					p Request recommendations for contacts with a particular background and have colleagues recommend current contacts who may fit your need.
			.row
				br
			.row.well
				.span8
					h4 Get started by logging in with your organization's Gmail.
				.span4
					a.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.pull-right(href='/authorize') Login with Gmail

